<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink309">
<l>vēṉiṟ ṟiṅkaḷ veñcura miṟantu</l>
<l>celavayarn taṉaiyā ṉīyē naṉṟu</l>
<l>niṉṉayan tuṟaivi kaṭuñcūṟ ciṟuvaṉ</l>
<l>muṟuval kāṇṭali ṉiṉitō</l>
<l>viṟuvarai nāṭanī yiṟantucey poruḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>You decided to go, leaving for the hot desert in the month of the heat. </l>
<l>This is fine! O man from the land of large mountains!</l>
<l>The wealth that you make by going [to the wasteland] –</l>
<l>is it more pleasant than the smile of [your] little son </l>
<l>[born] by your loving wife in her first pregnancy? </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
